title: Schedule A Tour To See Our Newly Renovated Apartment Homes/Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
